
* Challenges in work projects ? ======================
  - React dashboard started lagging whenever large datasets (10k+ rows) were rendered in tables. 
    Optimized it by implementing lazy loading, memoized pure components with React.memo, and used pagination instead of loading all rows at once.
  - Moved complex state management into Redux.
  - In a search feature, every keystroke was triggering an API call, putting unnecessary load on the backend and slowing down the UI. Fixed it using debouncing.
  

* Cookies → small data sent automatically with every HTTP request
* LocalStorage → persistent data stored in browser only (no expiry date, manual cleanup)
* SessionStorage → temporary data stored per tab/session (just like localStorage but tied to only single tab)


